      <title>财政部信函中隐藏着拒绝美国钢铁交易的理由</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/reasons-to-reject-us-steel-deal-are-buried-in-treasury-letter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据称，美国总统乔·拜登计划以国家安全为由，终止新日铁公司以 141 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司的计划。美国财政部 8 月份的一封信提供了这一理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/reasons-to-reject-us-steel-deal-are-buried-in-treasury-letter</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 18:42:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙办公室称新任总理将于周五上午公布</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/macron-office-says-new-premier-to-be-announced-friday-morning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统办公室周四晚间表示，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙将于周五早上通过声明任命新总理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/macron-office-says-new-premier-to-be-announced-friday-morning</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 18:40:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗起诉违反女性公开唱歌禁令的女子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/iran-prosecutes-woman-for-defying-ban-on-female-public-singing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗当局正在起诉一名女歌手，因其在违反宗教着装规定的情况下进行个人演唱直播 —— 这是伊朗伊斯兰共和国在面临国内外压力的情况下女性继续挑战的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/iran-prosecutes-woman-for-defying-ban-on-female-public-singing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 18:21:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监督机构称 FBI 线人未接到指示前往 1 月 6 日暴乱现场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/fbi-watchdog-discloses-use-of-informants-at-jan-6-capitol-riot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国司法部内部监督机构的报告，20多名联邦调查局线人参加了唐纳德·特朗普于 2021 年 1 月举行的集会，随后在美国国会大厦发生骚乱，以阻止总统选举认证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/fbi-watchdog-discloses-use-of-informants-at-jan-6-capitol-riot</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 18:03:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普顾问考虑将 SALT 抵扣限额提高至 20,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/trump-advisers-consider-raising-salt-write-off-limit-to-20-000</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普的经济顾问正在考虑将州和地方税收减免增加一倍，这是一项受欢迎但成本昂贵的税收减免政策，可以为纽约、新泽西和加利福尼亚的许多居民节省大笔开支。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/trump-advisers-consider-raising-salt-write-off-limit-to-20-000</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 17:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞击败巴尼耶为下任法国总理提供经验教训</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/how-le-pen-chewed-up-barnier-hold-lessons-for-next-french-pm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将卸任的法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶（Michel Barnier）学到了一个惨痛的教训，他的继任者也应该知道这一点。玛丽娜·勒庞（Marine Le Pen）是无法安抚的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/how-le-pen-chewed-up-barnier-hold-lessons-for-next-french-pm</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 17:11:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟与瑞士达成移民协议 更接近达成更广泛协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/eu-swiss-reach-immigration-accord-bringing-broader-deal-closer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，瑞士与欧盟在移民问题上达成妥协，克服了主要症结，并可能为达成新的双边关系协议铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/eu-swiss-reach-immigration-accord-bringing-broader-deal-closer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 16:51:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯即将与叙利亚新领导人达成保留军事基地的协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/russia-nears-deal-with-new-syria-leaders-to-keep-military-bases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯即将与叙利亚新领导层达成协议，保留其在中东国家的两个重要军事基地，这是克里姆林宫在其盟友巴沙尔·阿萨德倒台后的一个关键目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/russia-nears-deal-with-new-syria-leaders-to-keep-military-bases</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 14:21:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普“破坏性”能源关税不会带来赢家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/no-winners-seen-in-trump-s-hugely-destructive-energy-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当当选总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布计划对来自加拿大和墨西哥的商品征收关税，直至他们阻止移民和毒品的流动时，他表示他希望这些国家“付出巨大的代价！”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/no-winners-seen-in-trump-s-hugely-destructive-energy-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
